	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/jmx/JmxServerFactory.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/jmx/TrailLoggerMBean.java

	Added own package for testrecording stuff:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/ApplicationList.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/TestRecordingMBean.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/Application.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/TrailLogger.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/TestRecording.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/testrecording/TrailLoggerMBean.java

	Added PerfloggingMBean and did some refactoring (fixed generics warnings):
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/perflogging/PerfLogging.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/perflogging/Interval.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/perflogging/PerfStatistic.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/perflogging/LogFileWriterThread.java
