	Released Pfixcore 0.11.0

	* build.xml: Changed Pfixcore version

2007-07-27  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/dom/IncludePart.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/internal/CommonIncludePartImpl.java: 
