	editor. Allow new theme variant to be created even for non-existing parts.
	Made default theme variant deletable using editor.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGenerator.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/IncludeDocumentExtension.java: 
	Made default theme for new parts configurable: The last theme listed in the
	projects global theme list will be used as the default theme, however the
	"default" special theme will still be used as a fallback.
	
2007-07-27  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added object-to-xml mapping framework providing 
	support for easy result tree creation from arbitrary
	objects. Therefore the ResultDocument now provides
	additional addObject(...) methods. The object
	serialization can be customized by the bean
	annotations known from the JSON serialization
	mechanism. 

	Added object-to-xml mapping framework:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/MarshallingException.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/SerializerRegistry.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/SerializationContext.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/MarshallerFactory.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/ComplexTypeSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/SimpleTypeSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers/BeanSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers/CollectionSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers/MapSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers/ArraySerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/serializers/ObjectToStringSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/MarshallerImpl.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/DOMWriter.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/SerializationException.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/impl/XMLWriter.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/Marshaller.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/MappingException.java

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ResultDocument.java: Added addObject(...)
	methods to serialize objects into result tree

	Added object-xml-mapping sample to encoding test page:
	* projects/sample1/txt/pages/main_encoding.xml
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/ContextEncodingTestImpl.java 

	Added object-xml-mapping test:
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/oxm/Test.java
