	de.schlund.pfixcore.beans, cause it's no longer webservice specific
	and can be used by other parts of the framework and is used by the
	object-xml-mapping framework
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/beans
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/beans: Renamed the
	according test packages


2007-07-26  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Provide IWrapper information within XSLT at runtime.
	Therefore the new XSLT function pfx:getIWrapperInfo can
	be used to retrieve the XML fragment describing the
	IWrapper. The format is similar to the .iwrp file format.
	The function expects the IWrapper prefix name and the
	page name as parameters.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperInfo.java:
	this class extracts the IWrapper information and caches
	the resulting document
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperParam.java:
	fixed wrong casting from pre- to postcheck in getPostChecks
	method
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/TransformerCallback.java:
	added callback method to retrieve IWrapper description
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/Xml.java: make XSLT version
	detection publicly available
	* projects/core/build/iwrapper.xsl: generate IWrapper
	annotations into IWrapper sources
	* projects/core/xsl/functions.xsl: added pfx:getIWrapperInfo
	function
	* projects/sample1/txt/pages/main_iwrapperinfo.xml: added
	sample page which retrieves some IWrappers and its parameters
	* projects/sample1/conf/depend.xml: added sample page
	* projects/sample1/conf/config.conf.xml: added sample page

2007-07-25  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Fixed interface/IWrapper logging bugs: use FileResource instead
	of File for logging (using File failed because of pfixroot scheme
	in URI). Added method getOutputStream(boolean append) to FileResource
	interfaces/implementations (needed for appending logs). Fixed
	bug concerning logging of indexed params (NoSuchElementException due
	to iterator misusage).

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperImpl.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/resources/DocrootResourceImpl.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/resources/FileResource.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/resources/FileSystemResourceImpl.java

