	Improved copy & past in javascript editor form.

2007-07-16  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added support for automatic IWrapper generation from annotated beans.
	Everything which can be configured in XML within the iwrp-Files now
	can be done within Java bean classes by using according annotations.

	The Java source files now are preprocessed by the JDK's apt tool.
	Using the IWrapperAnnotationProcessor the Java IWrapper sources are
	generated from the beans by apt. 
	
	Added:

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/Param.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/PreCheck.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/Transient.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/Property.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/IWrapper.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/PostCheck.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/annotation/Caster.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/IWrapperGeneratorTask.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/IWrapperAnnotationProcessor.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/BeanDescriptor.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/MirrorApiUtils.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/IWrapperAnnotationProcessorFactory.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/iwrpgen/IWrapperRuntimeGenerator.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/CommonAnnotationProcessorFactory.java

	Modified: 

	* build.xml: precompile AnnotationProcessor stuff before generation
	* skel/build-skel.xml: added apt target before compile target

2007-07-03  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Performance improvements for client-side JSON Javascript webservice 
	stub usage:
	- Multiple Javascript webservice stubs now can be generated and delivered 
	as a single file
	- Javascript webservice stub files now can optionally be requested without
	a session id, thus the ETag/caching-mechanism works across sessions
	
	The pfx:wsscript tag now has an optional attribute session, indicating
	if the session id should be added to stub requests (default is false).
	The name attribute now can contain multiple service names separated by
	whitespace.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/ServiceRuntime.java: added support
	for generation of multiple stubs into one file
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/utils/FileCache.java: cleanup
	* projects/core/xsl/master.xsl: added support for multiple service
	names and sessionless usage to pfx:wsscript tag
	* projects/webservice/conf/depend.xml: removed encoding setting

2007-07-02  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/UserManagementServiceImpl.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/vo/EditorUser.java: 
	Use LinkedHashMaps instead of HashMaps to keep order of entries.

2007-06-29  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Removed generation of IWrapper method toString() and added generic
	toString()-implementation to class IWrapperImpl (simplification of
	generated code)

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperImpl.java
	* projects/core/build/iwrapper.xsl

2007-06-29  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/ContextImpl.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/SessionStatusEvent.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/SessionStatusListener.java: 
	Implemented session listeners: Applications can register a listener with a
	context instance that is notfied, when the session is invalidated.	

2007-06-27  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/config/impl/DirectOutputServletConfigImpl.java: fixed property
	customization problem, added support for customizable global and pagerequest 
	properties (incomplete CustomizationHandler initialization)

2007-06-21  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/context/RequestContextImpl.java: include __frame 
	parameter to reuse redirect URL (if existing)

2007-06-21  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* projects/core/xsl/forminput.xsl: bugfix: calling image geometry extension
	function with percentage values causes NumberFormatException, quickfix just
	copies width/height percentage values without calling the extension function
	for pfx:xinp@type='image' elements

2007-06-21  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Fixed changed trail logging behaviour: instead of reuse flag the new
	trailLogged flag in SPDocument is used to decide if a trail has to be logged.
	It's also used to for the logging of the result tree.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/SPDocument.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/AbstractXMLServer.java

2007-06-19  jtl  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/DumpText.java: Implement IDumptText. You can extend from DUmpText now and give 
	your extended class as an argument to the dumptext.sh. No need to copy the main method anymore
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/IDumpText.java: Helper interface to allow easier overwriting of
	the DumpText class.

2007-06-15  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

