	page object not having a target object. 

2007-06-04  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/ContextImpl.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/InvalidateSessionState.java: 
