	after the dumped text has been translated to make sure the tag structure is still the same)

2007-05-30  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/CheckIncludes.java: 
	Fixed bug causing check includes utility to use wrong path names
	
