2007-04-12  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added JSON serialization tests for Lists and Maps, e.g. unparameterized
	Lists and Maps, which can be serialized, but not deserialized due to
	missing type information.

	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/JSONSerializerTest.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/ReadOnlyBean.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/TestBean.java

2007-04-11  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added JSON (de-)serialization support for generic Lists and Maps. Because of
	the restrictions of the JSON format, especially the absence of type information,
	the support for Lists and Maps itself is restricted: Lists need a parameterized
	type parameter and this type has to be instantiable (or be a parameterized List
	or Map itself), the same with Map values, Map keys have to be java.lang.String 
	instances.

	Added:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/serializers/ListSerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/serializers/MapSerializer.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/JSONSerializerTest.java
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/TestBean.java

	Modified:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/webservices/TypeTestImpl.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/webservices/TypeTest.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/SerializerRegistry.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/DeserializerRegistry.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/JSONDeserializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/serializers/ArraySerializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/SerializationContext.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/Deserializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/JSONWSProcessor.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/deserializers/ArrayDeserializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/deserializers/BooleanDeserializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/deserializers/BeanDeserializer.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/jsonws/deserializers/StringDeserializer.java
