2007-03-16  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added new IWrapper definition attribute 'implements', which
	produces an according 'implements' declaration in the generated 
	class and can be used to tag IWrappers, e.g. for common handling
	of IWrappers which can't have a common base class, but have a
	set of common fields, which should be handled by the same method.

	* projects/core/build/iwrapper.xsl
	* projects/core/schema/interfacewrapper200401.xsd

