	* projects/webservice/xml/two_frames.xml: 
	* projects/core/img/console_webserviceadmin.gif: 
	* projects/core/img/console_webservicemonitor.gif: 
	* projects/core/xsl/utils.xsl: 
	Redesigned links for webservice console using icons now.

2006-12-21  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ImageGeometry.java: 
	* projects/core/xsl/forminput.xsl: 
	* projects/core/xsl/include.xsl: 
	Use CSS style attribute instead of width/height attribute to be compatible
	with W3C's HTML specifications for <input type="image" .../> tag.
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/config/includes/IncludesResolver.java (resolveIncludes): 
	Fixed typo causing "refid" not to work.

2006-12-15  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>
	
