	* skel/build-skel.xml: let clean-webservice target remove
	generated WSDL and JS stuff too

2006-11-21  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/ServiceRuntime.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/DefaultAuthIWrapperState.java: 
