	implement it.

2006-08-23  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/ContextImpl.java
	(ContextImpl::documentFromFlow): don't think pageflow that is set
	because the variant may have changed is also user requested. This
	broke MANY pages :-(
	

