	(ServletManager::createTestCookie) 
	(ServletManager::redirectToSecureSSLSession)
	(ServletManager::doGet) changed to work with setCookiePath, and to
	cleanup Cookies if needed (more than 10 sec session cookies, or
	cookies too old.)

