	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ContextXMLServer.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/DependencyTracker.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/DerefServer.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/DirectOutputServlet.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/FactoryInitServlet.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ImageGeometry.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ImageGeometryData.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ImageThemedSrc.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/IncludeDocument.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/IncludeDocumentExtension.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/IncludeDocumentFactory.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ProjectInitFactory.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ResultDocument.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ServletManager.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/util/statuscodes/StatusCode.java: 
	* lib/commons-logging-1.0.4.jar: 
	* projects/common/conf/factory.xml: 
	* projects/core/build/create_webxml.xsl: 
	* projects/webservice/xml/two_frames.xml: 
	* skel/build-skel.xml: 
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGeneratorTest.java: 
	* tests/junit/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/XsltTest.java: 
	Deprecated PathFactory in favor of the new ResourceUtil class which provides
	a cleaner and more universal approach to access file resources. However
	the PathFactory and its corresponding Path class can still be used by 
	application developers, although they are disencouraged to do so. Pfixcore
	itself does not use the PathFactory any more.
	The Xslt#loadTemplates(...) methods now are not synchronized. Instead the
	TransformerFactory is stored in ThreadLocal.

2006-08-03  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Replaced json.org and json-rpc libraries by our own
	JSON parsing/serialization/deserialization implementations.

	The new package de.schlund.pfixcore.webservice.json contains
	a JSON parser and an abstract Java model representing JSON
	data (replaces the json.org library).

	The new package de.schlund.pfixcore.webservice.jsonws contains
	a JSON serialization/deserialization framework and a ServiceProcessor
	implementation (replaces the json-rpc library).

	Modified:

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/webservices/chat/Message.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/webservices/TypeTest.java
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/webservice/ServiceDescriptor.java
