2006-04-21  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperParam.java
	(IWrapperParam::setValue) new method, used internally and for
	usage when testig.
	
	(IWrapperParam::setStringValue(RequestParam[])): removed. handled
	(IWrapperParam::setSimpleObjectValue(Object[])): renamed to 
	IWrapperParam::setStringValue(Object[]). This now also handles the
	RequestParam case.

