2006-04-19  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java
	(Context::checkIsAccessible): always try to update the navigation
	here, too (in case it will be reused)

	(Context::addNavigation, Context::recursePages): bugfixes to make
	reuse of navigation possible at last. This hasn't been working for
	a long time it seems.

