	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/DefaultIWrapperState.java (DefaultIWrapperState::getDocument): 
	implemented to set autoinvalidate_navi to false when
	isDirectTrigger returns true (this is to share the navigation as
	long as there has (for sure) no data been submitted that may have
	changed the data model) 

