	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java:
	removed adminmode implementation - never needed anyway, and just
	too stupid to be useful.

	(handleRequest)
	(handleRequestWorker): now handleRequest makes sure in a finally
	block to reset a saved variant and autoinvalidate state after the request.

	(setAutoinvalidateNavigationForRequest): can be used to set the
	autoinvalidation of the navigation structure for this request.
	
