2006-03-18  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/IWrapperSimpleContainer.java
	(IWrapperSimpleContainer::stayAfterSubmit): remove handling of
	SUGGESTCONT command (never used anyway)	
