	handling of DESELWRP command (never used anyway)

2006-03-16  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java (Context): added
	the ability to set a variant only for one request, and restore the 
	"old" variant on the next incoming request. We do it this way to
	make sure that even in case of an exception, we still know what
	variant is the "permanent" one (without the need to catch every exception).
	(Context::setVariantForThisRequestOnly): new method
	(Context::setVariant): when there is already a variant set for
	only the current request, use the given variant for the following requests instead.

