2006-02-27  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* build.xml: 
	* skel/build-skel.xml: changed to remove the CVS_AUTOTAG stuff,
	no longer have a notag target. Now, on "ant dist", we simply put the output of "svn info" into
