2006-02-23  Sebastian Marsching  <sebastian.marsching@1und1.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/AbstractXMLServer.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/DocrootServlet.java: 
	* example/core/build/create_serverxml.xsl: 
	* example/core/build/create_webxml.xsl: 
	* example/core/xsl/forminput.xsl: 
	* example/core/xsl/include.xsl: 
	* example/core/xsl/master.xsl: 
	* example/core/xsl/navigation.xsl: 
	* example/core/xsl/utils.xsl: 
	Changed the XSL templates to prepend the context path to constructed URLs
	in order to allow WAR names other than xml.war. In order to make this also
	work in standalone mode, the servlets are now directly running in the root
	context of each vhost instead of the special /xml subcontext and servlet
	mappings have been changed to keep known URLs.

