	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGenerator.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/VirtualTarget.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/Xslt.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/DependencyTracker.java: 
	Making AuxDependency an interface and implementing the different types
	in sub-classes
	
	* example/core/build/create_depend.xsl: 
	Removing <depaux> tags where possible, as these dependencies are now
	detected automatically
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/internal/TargetPfixImpl.java (getAuxDependencies): 
	Adapting method to retrieve aux targets using AuxDependencyManager
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/frontend/resources/TargetsResourceImpl.java (renderTarget): 
	Handling dependencies for leaf targets
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/Xslt.java: 
	Adapting FileResolver to store target dependencies within the
	aux dependency manager of the generated target
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/AuxDependency.java: 
	Handling aux dependencies of type target
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/AuxDependencyManager.java (addDependency): 
	Handling target type dependencies and dependendencies for leaf targets, the
	latter by creating .aux files within the target generator's cache directory
	for leaf target files
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/DependencyType.java: 
	Adding dependency type target
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/LeafTarget.java: 
	Adding code to manage auxiliary dependencies (like stylesheet includes) in
	leaf targets
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGenerator.java: 
	Changing tryReinit() to always use path to configuration file supplied
	during construction
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGeneratorFactory.java (createGenerator): 
	Adapting call of TargetGenerator#tryReinit() to new signature
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetRW.java: 
	Removing registerTargetDependency() method as it is not used any more
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetImpl.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/VirtualTarget.java: 
	Moving AuxDependencyManager from VirtualTarget to TargetImpl, so that it
	is available in LeafTarget
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XMLLeafTarget.java: 
	Adding dummy AuxDependencyManager to satisfy TargetImpl
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XSLLeafTarget.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XSLVirtualTarget.java: 
	Using AuxDependencyManager to store target dependencies
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/AbstractXMLServer.java (tryReloadProperties): 
	Adapting call of TargetGenerator#tryReinit() to new signature

