2006-01-09  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>
	(forgot to comitt ChangeLog)
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/VirtualTarget.java (VirtualTarget::needsUpdate): 
	we shouldn't call getModtimeMaybeUpdate in needsUpdate - this is intended to be a 
	low overhead method to determine if you need an update at all.

