2006-01-03  Michael Hartmeier <mhm@schlund.de>

	* switch to tomcat 5.5:
	  o adjust server.xml
	  o use jdk xerces instead of tomcat xerces (because 5.5 doesn't have one)
	  o specify xsd instead of doctype
	  o xmlValidation="false" - tomcat didn't accept our web.xmls with neither xsd nor dtd

