	Adding method that returns DOM tree for any target type
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetRW.java: Making interface public
	so that it can be used by the Xslt utility class
	(registerTargetDependency): Added method to register a dependency on another
	Target for the current target

