	* example/sample1/txt/navigation.xml (Module): 
	* example/sample1/conf/depend.xml.in (Module): 
	* example/sample1/xsl/generatedruntime.xsl (Module): changed generated stylesheet 
	example to use metatags.xsl so we can demonstrate the use of pfx:include to generate a 
	stylesheet from include parts.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java (Context::documentFromFlow): 
	also run flow step actions when prohibitcontinue is already set. This shouldn't change 
	much currently, but allows to define new actions that also make sense when the page remains the same

