	use TargetDependencyRelation to get list of affected targets, guard against null values

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/internal/ProjectImpl.java (ProjectImpl::getAllImages): 
	use TargetDependencyRelation to get the project dependencies for the spezified type. Guard against
	null values.
	(ProjectImpl::findIncludePartThemeVariant): ...and to get all project dependencies
	(ProjectImpl::hasIncludePart): ...and to get the list of affected TargetGenerators

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/internal/IncludePartThemeVariantImpl.java 
	(IncludePartThemeVariantImpl::getIncludeDependencies): use TargetDependencyRelation to get the overall 
	children for the AuxDependency, guard against null return value.
	(IncludePartThemeVariantImpl::getImageDependencies): ditto.
	(IncludePartThemeVariantImpl::getImageDependencies): use aux.getTheme()
