	Added method for writing ChangeLog entries
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/core/spring/internal/CommonIncludePartThemeVariantImpl.java (setXML): 
	Added call to protected method writeChangeLog() which creates an editor
	ChangeLog entry in the child classes
	(setXML): Update exactly one page synchronously in order to make changes visible

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/frontend/resources/CommonIncludesResourceImpl.java
	setContent(): Use Xml.parseStringMutable() instead of
	Xml.parseString() as the latter caused problems with namespaces
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor2/frontend/resources/CommonIncludesResource.java
	setContent(): Throwing SAXException instead of TransformerException due to
	changes in the implementation (see above)
	
