	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/RefCountingCollectionIterator.java (Module):
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/util/RefCountingCollection.java (Module):
	Implementation of the Collection interface that stores for each
	member a counter - adding the same element again increases,
	removing it decreases the counter, until it reaches 0, at which point the whole 
	element is removed from the collection.

