2005-11-08  Benjamin Reitzammer <benjamin@schlund.de>

	* skel/build-skel.xml - added build-tasks for modules mechanism. All *.jar files 
	located in modules-directory are automatically unjarred into projects/modules.
	It's best to pack the files in the modules *.jar files into their own direcotory
	so they don't incidentally overwrite files from other modules

