2005-10-05  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	* skel/build.xml: Renamed target 'tomcat.defaultwebxml' to 'defaultwebxml' and
	placed it after the init-data target (so that 'create_defaultwebxml.xsl' is 
	already extracted).

2005-10-05  Martin Leidig  <mleidig@schlund.de>

	Added customization support for Tomcat's default 'web.xml' to the build process.
	After extracting Tomcat the new target 'tomcat.defaultwebxml' is called, which
	transforms the default 'web.xml' using the stylesheet 'create_defaultwebxml.xsl'.
	At the moment the stylesheet only sets the 'listings' init parameter of the
	default servlet to 'false' (disabling directory listings) and leaves the rest
	unchanged.

	* skel/build.xml: Added new target 'tomcat.defaultwebxml'
	* example/core/build/create_defaultwebxml.xsl: Added file

