2005-07-25  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/Context.java: PageMessages are now also implemented in 
	terms of StatusCodeInfo objects.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapper.java: addScodeWithArgs: removed.
	only one addScode method to handle everything

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperImpl.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperIndexedParam.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperParam.java: use StatusCodeInfo, remove all but one 
	fully qualified version of addSCode

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperParamCheck.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/SimpleCheck.java: StatusCodeInfo instead of StatusCode used
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/DefaultAuthIWrapperState.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/IWrapperSimpleContainer.java: use resdoc instead of resform,
	also use StatusCodeInfo where needed.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ResultDocument.java (Module): added public (and useful) methods from ResultForm

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ResultForm.java (Module): removed. Methods are now in ResultDocument

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/example/TShirtHandler.java: cosmetics 

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/StatusCodeInfo.java (Module): new class. Used to hold the scode
	and it's associated meta information (arguments, level)

