2005-07-12  Niels Schelbach    <niels@schlund.de>

	* example/core/build/create_propfiles.xsl: added conversion of <interceptor @class="some.class"/> to context.(start|end)interceptor.($formattednumber)=some.class
	see schema change
	* example/core/schema/properties200401.xsd: added new toplevel tag: interceptors right after the context element:
	an example:
	...
	</context>
	<interceptors>
	   <start>
	      <interceptor class="some.start.interceptor.class"/>
	   </start>   
	   <end>
	      <interceptor class="some.end.interceptor.class"/>
	   </end>   
	</interceptors>
	...  
	*	example/sample1/conf/config.prop.in: adopted the config.prop.in to the new convience Tag
	
