	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperParam.java (compareTo): changed to allow comparisons 
	with all IWrapperParamDefinitions
	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/generator/IWrapperIndexedParam.java (compareTo): new method

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/app/IWrapperSimpleContainer.java (addIWrapperStatus): set 
	the docheck=false attribute for wrappers that return a null object for gimmeAllParamDefinitions()

	* example/core/xsl/metatags.xsl.in: 
	* example/core/xsl/master.xsl.in: 
