	I assume that the logic for permission handling needs some banging, too - but we'll
	see this in real live.
	
	* example/core/editor/conf/depend.xml.in: include runtime stylesheet for targets, too 

2005-04-24  Jens Lautenbacher  <jtl@schlund.de>
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/AuxDependencyManager.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/AuxDependency.java: 
	Completely rewrote the way the parent-child relation of auxdependencies are stored.
	we now store the childs seperate for each themes spec. Also the affected targets are stored locally 
	in the AuxDependency itself, so no need anymore to store a link to the parent.
	Basically all of this should fix a bug that has been there forever, but only with the new variants 
	happens much more often.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/PageTargetTree.java (getPageInfoForPageName): new method
	(addEntry): now store also a mapping of page name to all pageinfos with that name (aka all variants)

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetGenerator.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetFactory.java: 
	all Target creation now needs a themes argument. Use the new Themes type.

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XSLVirtualTarget.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XSLLeafTarget.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XMLLeafTarget.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/XMLVirtualTarget.java: contructors need Themes parameter 

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetImpl.java (setThemes): removed
	(getThemes): now return type Themes
	(getThemesString): removed
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/Target.java (getThemes): now return type Themes
	(getThemesString): removed

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/VirtualTarget.java (setThemes): removed
	changed according to new Themes class
	
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/TargetRW.java: 
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/LeafTarget.java (setThemes): removed 

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/workflow/StateImpl.java: cosmetics

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/Themes.java (Module):
	added. Themes aggregate the String[] of fallback themes, and the
	id string (just all themes space separated). This will be contructed one time only.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/IncludeDocumentExtension.java:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ImageThemedSrc.java:
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/AbstractXMLServer.java: changed accordingly

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/targets/DependencyParent.java (Module): removed 

	* example/sample1/txt/pages/main_home.xml: added small stuff to demo themes again

	* src/de/schlund/pfixcore/editor/interfaces/Includes.iwrp: 
