2004-10-22  Michael Hartmeier  <mhm@schlund.de>

	* Dump status code property files, always use dyntxt/statusmessages.xml.
	* Removed res.jar files. Instead, the compile target copies the res directory (if there
	is one) into the build directory.
	* Removed FactoryInit base class, the init method is called via reflection now.
	(Rationale: dependency on FactoryInit class was problematic because it's
	from util.jar)

