2004-07-26 Joerg Haecker <haecker@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/PfixServletRequest.java: removed newline for
	perf-logging.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ServletManager.java(getExceptionConfigForThrowable):
	log classnotfound-exceptions.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/exceptionprocessor/util/ExceptionDataValueHelper.java:
	ignore all exceptions when calling session-values.toString. This leads
	to a strange behaviour when having a 'normal' exception and also an
	exceptions in a toString-method in a contextresource.

