2004-07-20 Michael Hartmier  <mhm@schlund.de>
	- switched to tomcat 5:
	  the 'example/servletconf/tomcat' directory is not longer checked-in,
          instead it's generated automatically from lib/tomcat/jakarta-tomcat-*.tgz.
	  Thus, we can upgrade to a new version by replacing the tgz file.
        - tomcat configuration changes:
	  - http and https connectors are configured: you can run a standalone tomcat without apache
          - tomcat manager is configured and can be accessed from web apps via a console button
          - server.xml is generated with relative paths
        - examples/core/build/ changes:
          - the xsl "container" parmeter has been removed
          - the defpath declaration is used for apache.conf and server.xml generation now
	- fix redirect code for ports != 80/443
	- affected files:
	* .classpath
	* ChangeLog
	* build.xml
	* example/core/build/create_apacheconf.xsl
	* example/core/build/create_lib.xsl
	* example/core/build/create_serverxml.xsl
	* example/core/img/manager.gif
	* example/core/xsl/include.xsl.in
	* example/servletconf/.cvsignore
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/.cvsignore
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/bin/bootstrap.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/bin/catalina.sh
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/bin/setclasspath.sh
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/common/lib/commons-collections.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/common/lib/jndi.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/common/lib/naming-common.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/common/lib/naming-resources.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/common/lib/servlet.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/conf/.cvsignore
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/logs/.cvsignore
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/catalina.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/commons-beanutils.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/commons-digester.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/commons-logging.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/jakarta-regexp-1.3.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/servlets-common.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/servlets-default.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/servlets-invoker.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/servlets-manager.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/servlets-webdav.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/tomcat-http11.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/tomcat-jk.jar
	* example/servletconf/tomcat/server/lib/tomcat-util.jar
