2004-07-19  Benjamin Reitzammer <benjamin@schlund.de>

	* added src/de/schlund/pfixcore/util/XsltCustomWebXmlTask.java
	* added example/core/conf/web.xml
	* added example/core/build/create_customtomcatweb.xsl
	when the XsltCustomWebXmlTask is used instead of the XsltWebXmlTask, it is
	detected at build time, if a project has a custom web.xml in it's conf folder.
	If this is the case, this custom web.xml is used as a source document for the
	transformation with create_customtomcatweb.xsl. If there is no custom web.xml
	in the project's conf folder, the web.xml file in conf/core will be used as
	source document.

2004-07-13  Joerg Haecker <haecker@schlund.de>

	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/PerfEventType.java: removed
	get/setMessage method. Added get/setPage and
	get/setHandlingClass instead.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/PfixServletRequest.java:
	improved perfstat-logging. see above.
	* src/de/schlund/pfixxml/ServletManager.java
